section.section-questions
  .section-questions--content
    p.intro.regular-bold
      | 8/28，台灣即將舉行核四公投，但你真的了解核四嗎？ <br />
      | 試試下面這個小測驗， 看看核四是否跟你想像中的一樣！

    h1 #{greeting}

    div.splide.question-slider
      div.splide__track
        ul.splide__list

          - lastIndex = questions.length - 1
          each item, i in questions
            li.splide__slide
              div.question.card.question-box(data-answer=`a${item.answer}`)
                p.question.regular-bold Q#{i + 1}.#{item.question}
                div.option-list
                  each option, j in item.options
                    button.option-list-item.button.regular-bold(data-value=`a${j}`)
                      if j === item.answer
                        img(src="../images/question_yes.svg", width="21", height="22", alt="")
                      else
                        img(src="../images/question_no.svg", width="18", height="17", alt="")
                      | #{option}

            li.splide__slide
              div.card.answer-detail
                p.button.regular-bold #{item.options[item.answer]}
                p.regular-bold #{item.detail}
                div.btn-holder
                  if i === lastIndex
                      a.button-next-section.regular-bold.button-black(href="#section-reasons")
                        include ../images/down_arror.svg
                        | 為何不該續建核四
                  else
                      button.button-next-quetion.regular-bold.button-black 下一題
